default  More than one in five peo
defaultple in West Somerset live beyond the ‘reasonable’ limit for accessing key services via public transport, with the exception of hospitals and primary schools.  Only 26% of residents live where they can either walk or get public transport to access their
default loc
defaultal
default town centre. 
